{"word":"ἐξαρπάζω","slug":"ἐξαρπάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξαρπάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ξω</el>) (<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>,) (also <el>-άσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐξήρπαξα</el>) (or <el>-ασα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to snatch away from</i> a place, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; <el>τι παρά τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>τι ἐκ χερῶν τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>:— <i>to rescue</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>οἱ ἐξηρπασμένοι</el> <i>the captured ones</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to tear out</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}